{"tid":1246100,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點樣先為之係不合作運動？","createTime":"2019-06-20T14:39:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T15:32:05.000Z","uid":38966,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a4607f28359020226f9bcbfd811bb61e3521cdfb","tid":1246100,"uid":38966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T14:39:46.000Z","msg":"我地一齊回顧下以前革命嘅案例<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n捷克斯洛伐克嘅天鵝絨革命(遊行示威)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n防暴警察在布拉格鎮壓學生示威。該事件引發了從11月19日到12月下旬的一系列示威，真正示威開始到成功用左1個月多嘅時間。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n亞美尼亞示威(不合作運動)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">癱瘓交通</span></span><br />\n1)十幾人至幾十人為單位係城市各處自發堵路，而且在警察執法時大多都會配合離去（但去附近重新堵路）<br />\n2)用合理速度橫過行人優先嘅班馬線，或在守法情況下不斷橫過馬路（係香港，15米內沒有合適過路設施，中間又沒有欄杆路障，就可以直接橫過馬路）。<br />\n3)鐘意踩單車嘅人，都可以係馬路上面合法騎行，只要保持單行（但可以佔據一條行車線保障自己安全），而且入黑後配有頭燈尾燈即可。乘客搭地鐵也有權力及理由在月台靜候舒適和有空位可坐嘅列車。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n法國黃背心運動(暴力抗爭)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1)<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">特定時間，不同地點</span></span><br />\n佢地逢週六湧上街，地點路線不定，不死守任何公共空間，不預先公佈時間下快閃式堵路。譬如堵塞高速公路和迴旋處，接管或燒毀道路收費站，等汽車自由通行，令政府無利可圖。<br />\n2)<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">以錯誤訊息攻其不備</span></span><br />\n係時間上創造優勢，譬如模糊確實嘅行動日期時間，達到攻其不備嘅效果。<br />\n3)<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">靈活運用抗爭者</span></span><br />\n突襲佔領重要的權力地標，開放予公眾集會(和理非)，但半夜出其不意棄守陣地，轉戰其他地方，以虛耗防暴警察的資源。"},{"pid":"89c8abbd15d1db7da11a5fef1758755c5c2ea93c","tid":1246100,"uid":38966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T14:40:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"db3a5e5d8a088aee200234178a02524519d8e8fd","tid":1246100,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T14:40:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>突發！！！驚現「賣港」三人組</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4yLdRw0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4yLdRw0.jpg&h=a32fbdc4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">----分隔----</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LCaM3o3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLCaM3o3.png&h=e65f7020&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7724c2373b807920e2f183034ca79cbe19540ff3","tid":1246100,"uid":38966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T14:42:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"827b962927e2a74aa06d3e95065bd006c16ce3f9","tid":1246100,"uid":38177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T14:44:41.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"639b18429d838a2954d445cea23283731d864364","tid":1246100,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T14:45:09.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7a6a34be284845a5d568df5df32f98b9b53d4809","tid":1246100,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T14:45:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd3c82684c733a6b0fe8f9e0c5b5b8efb85584ef","tid":1246100,"uid":38177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T14:46:53.000Z","msg":"依幾招都好好用，踩單車加過馬路都唔錯"},{"pid":"5831fa654e1c01fd9e6c6528142f5d75930d6f31","tid":1246100,"uid":38177,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T14:47:42.000Z","msg":"燒收費站好似有啲難度，不過最幫到市民🤝"},{"pid":"fcc939dcecd1f0556231cadbd31d8fae305fe422","tid":124610